, are of great interest for observations of low-mass young\nstellar objects with the Herschel Space Observatory. [OI] (at 63 and 145 mic)\nand [CII] (at 158 mic) fine structure emission are only affected for L_X >\n10^30 erg/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Nov 2010 13:35:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2010 09:16:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
